<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649870>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–24. Neotheronia altacima sp. nov., ♀: 20—head, dorso-postero-lateral; 21—propodeum, dorsal. Neotheronia bonita sp. nov., ♀: 22—propodeum, dorsal; 23—hind tarsus, lateral. Neotheronia charli, ♀: 24—propodeum, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649884>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37–41. Neotheronia mellosa, ♀: 37—head, dorso-postero-lateral. Neotheronia rosai, ♀: 38—head, antero-ventral; 39—mesosoma, dorsal. Neotheronia tacubaya, ♀: 40—propodeum, dorsal. Neotheronia tequila sp. nov., ♀: 41—head, front." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649856>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–7. Neotheronia tacubaya, ♀: 3—head, front; 4—propodeum, dorso-posterior. Neotheronia tequila sp. nov., holotype, ♀: 5—head, dorso-postero-lateral; 6—habitus (without apices of antennae and wings), lateral; 7—head and mesosoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649856/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649880>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31–36. Neotheronia lineata, ♀: 31, 32—propodeum, dorsal. Neotheronia veracruzana, ♀ (Tamaulipas): 33—head, dorso-posterior; 34—mesoscutum, dorsal; 35—propodeum, dorsal; 36—posterior part of metasoma, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649876>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–30. Neotheronia jugaldei, ♀: 25—pronotum, lateral; 26—mesopleuron, front. Neotheronia montezuma, ♀ (27– 29) and ♂ (30): 27—head, front; 28—pronotum, lateral; 29—mesopleuron, front; 30—metasoma, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649868>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–19. Neotheronia juanitae sp. nov., holotype, ♀: 16—apex of metasoma with ovipositor, lateral; 17—hind leg, lateral. Neotheronia zaldivari sp. nov., holotype, ♀: 18—head, antero-lateral; 19—mid and hind legs, lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4649868/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

